Key Match Events: Harry Kane scored a brace to secure victory for England
Post-Match Reflections: Harry Kane spoke about his 100th cap and his career
Miscellaneous Highlights: England remained unbeaten against Finland, with this their 10th victory across their 12 meetings
Others: Lille’s Angel Gomes became the first player to start for England while playing for a French club since Marseille’s Trevor Steven in June 1992
